membership:
One more remark on the list of countries above:&#xd;
We have different types of members, as described above (individuals, choirs, organisations). We do not have member organisations in all EU-member countries, but we do have members of one of the three types in all EU member countries. The countries I added are countries in which we have member organisations. In addition we have individual members and member choirs in other countries, including associate members in about 10 non-European countries. &#xd;
&#xd;
The European Choral Association - Europa Cantat is itself member of &#xd;
- the International Federation for Choral Music (IFCM -   http://ifcm.net)&#xd;
- the International and European Music Council (IMC - www.imc-cim.org /EMC - www.emc-imc.org)&#xd;
- Musica International (www.musicanet.org/en/home)&#xd;
- the Choral Festival Network (www.choralfestivalnetwork.org)&#xd;
- Culture Action Europe (http://cultureactioneurope.org)&#xd;
and is thus also connected to the choral world outside Europe and to other music and culture organisations.

